description: Demolition of retail store, industrial/warehouse buildings and lock-up garages; erection as phased development of new retail store; stepped 5-9 storey (plus lower ground floor) residential building comprising 83 units (73 private; 10 shared ownership) at eastern end of site; part 4, part 5-storey residential building comprising 32 affordable units near western end of site; servicing, car parking, cycle parking, new vehicular and pedestrian accesses, refuse/recycling area and landscaping
